- content_for :title do "Report a Player" end

%section
    .page-header
        %h2
            Report a User
            %a.btn.btn-primary.pull-right{:href => reports_path}
                %i.fa.fa-tasks
                All Reports
    .row
        .col-md-4
            %h4.strong Evidence
            %p Moderators <em>may not</em> punish based on screenshots, unless the alleged offense is chat-related (Discord or the forums).
        .col-md-4
            %h4.strong Make your videos unlisted
            %p If you will use footage as evidence, make your videos <strong>unlisted</strong>, not public or private.
            %p This ensures that the staff, and only the staff, will be able to view your video.
        .col-md-4
            %h4.strong Thanks for your hard work
            %p The staff appreciates the time you take to gather evidence of rule-breakers.
            %p Thanks for your commitment to making this community a better place!
    %br
    .row
        .col-md-12{:style => "text-align: center;"}
            %h3.strong Who are you reporting?
            .form-inline
                %input.typeahead.form-control#reports{:name => "search", :type => "text", :style => "margin-top: 0;"}
